PEER-REVIEW ACCESS LICENSE

This repository is provided to support peer review of the associated manuscript submitted to Digital Discovery (Royal Society of Chemistry).

Permitted uses during peer review:
- Inspection, evaluation, and discussion of the contents by the editor, referees, and Digital Discovery editorial staff for the purpose of evaluating the manuscript.

The final licensing terms for the public archival release will be specified upon acceptance and on deposition of the frozen release at Zenodo.

